interpretation: The woman supervillain emoji represents a powerful and cunning female antagonist. She embodies the archetype of the femme fatale, using her charm and intelligence to manipulate and control those around her. This card may indicate a situation where someone is using their wits and charisma to gain an advantage, or it may represent the shadow side of the querent's own personality - a tendency to be manipulative or deceitful. It can also represent a fear of being controlled or dominated by someone else. Keywords associated with this card include: manipulation, power, intelligence, danger, seduction, control, and deceit. When this card appears in a reading, it is important to consider the motives and intentions of those involved and to be aware of any potential power struggles or conflicts. The woman supervillain reminds us that sometimes the greatest threat comes from those closest to us, and that we must always be vigilant in protecting ourselves and our interests.
